{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.etaReduceAll\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">etaReduceAll</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Applies `etaReduce` to all subexpressions. Returns `e` unchanged if no subexpression is eta-reducible. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.etaReduceAll","kind":"def","line":86,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.etaReduceAll","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.lean#L86-L90"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.etaReduceWithCache\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">etaReduceWithCache</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Std.HashMap\">Std.HashMap</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/ExprPtr.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.ExprPtr\">ExprPtr</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> (<a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Std.HashMap\">Std.HashMap</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/ExprPtr.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.ExprPtr\">ExprPtr</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.etaReduceWithCache","kind":"def","line":62,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.etaReduceWithCache","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.lean#L62-L84"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.isEtaReducible\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">isEtaReducible</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns `true` if `e` can be eta-reduced. Uses pointer equality for efficiency. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.isEtaReducible","kind":"def","line":58,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.isEtaReducible","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.lean#L58-L60"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.etaReduce\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">etaReduce</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `e` is of the form `(fun x₁ ... xₙ => f x₁ ... xₙ)` and `f` does not contain `x₁`, ..., `xₙ`,\nthen returns `f`. Otherwise, returns `e`.\n\nReturns the original expression when not reducible to enable pointer equality checks.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.etaReduce","kind":"def","line":44,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.etaReduce","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Eta.lean#L44-L56"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Basic","Lean.Meta.Sym.ExprPtr","Lean.Meta.Transform"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Eta"}